1. *Uzbuđen* sam zbog koncerta koji će se održati večeras. (I'm excited about the concert that's taking place tonight.)
2. On je bio *uzbuđen* zbog pobjede svog tima. (He was excited about his team's victory.)
3. *Uzbuđenost* se mogla vidjeti na njegovom licu dok je otvarao poklon. (Excitement could be seen on his face as he opened the present.)
4. Nisam mogao zaspati jer sam bio previše *uzbuđen*. (I couldn't sleep because I was too excited.)
5. Osjećaj *uzbuđenosti* mi je prolazio kroz tijelo dok sam se penjao na vrh planine. (A feeling of excitement was coursing through my body as I climbed to the top of the mountain.)
6. Oni su *uzbuđeni* zbog putovanja koje su planirali za ovaj vikend. (They are excited about the trip they have planned for this weekend.)
7. Morao sam duboko udahnuti kako bih se smirio zbog *uzbuđenja* koje sam osjećao prije govora. (I had to take a deep breath to calm myself down from the excitement I was feeling before the speech.)
8. *Uzbuđenjem* su se svi igrači okupili na terenu prije početka utakmice. (With excitement, all the players gathered on the field before the start of the game.)
9. Kako bih smanjio svoju *uzbuđenost*, odlučio sam meditirati prije važnog sastanka. (To reduce my excitement, I decided to meditate before an important meeting.)
10. *Uzbuđen* sam što ću posjetiti novu zemlju i upoznati nove ljude. (I'm excited to visit a new country and meet new people.)